---
import portfolioData from "../data/portfolio.json";

const { email, phone, location } = portfolioData.personalInfo;
---

<div class="panel-contact">
  <div class="contact-cv-info">
    <p class="contact-cv-desc">
      Si quieres charlar, hacerme alguna consulta sobre mis proyectos o simplemente ponerte en contacto, podés escribirme directamente por cualquiera de estos medios:
    </p>
    
    <div class="contact-cv-details">
      <div class="contact-detail-item">
        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
        <a href={`mailto:${email}`} class="detail-link">{email}</a>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-detail-item">
        <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
        <span>{phone}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-detail-item">
        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
        <span>{location}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-wsp-action">
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/542346614492?text=Hola%20Bernardo!%20Vengo%20desde%20tu%20web." 
      target="_blank" 
      rel="noopener noreferrer" 
      class="btn btn-primary btn-submit-cv"
    >
      Contactar por WhatsApp <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
    </a>
    <a 
      href={`tel:${phone.replace(/\s+/g, '')}`} 
      class="btn btn-secondary btn-submit-cv btn-call-mobile"
    >
      Llamar por Teléfono <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .panel-contact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .contact-cv-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-cv-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .contact-detail-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .contact-detail-item i {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    width: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .detail-link {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-speed) ease;
  }

  .detail-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-wsp-action {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-submit-cv {
    width: 100%;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.25rem;
  }
</style>
